        "timestamp": "2020-01-23 12:09:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nFor example if you add ingress.enable to the VID in the onap-all.yaml:\n\n$ diff -Naur onap-all.yaml onap-all2.yaml\n--- onap-all.yaml       2020-01-22 10:24:51.315371818 +0000\n+++ onap-all2.yaml      2020-01-23 12:08:15.082098583 +0000\n@@ -74,6 +74,8 @@\n   enabled: true\n vid:\n   enabled: true\n+  ingress:\n+    enabled: true\n vnfsdk:\n   enabled: true\n modeling:",
